style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heirasti\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/829e36e9a5fabe9c444d447e46dd0cd1?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/829e36e9a5fabe9c444d447e46dd0cd1?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/heirasti\" class=\"reviewer-name\">heirasti</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 15, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We had it in use for a while but now we are fed up and deleted it.\nEvery update brought new issues.\n\nThe last thing (after we upgraded to V2) we spended hours with that menace was a language issue.\nWe found the most stupid strings on our german website like \"Previous Veranstaltung\" and others.\nAnd it was even impossible to change it since there is no equivalent in the .po-file</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">No shortcode</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dharma23\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5428dd28e50032e26b573f7f9a088a27?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/5428dd28e50032e26b573f7f9a088a27?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/dharma23\" class=\"reviewer-name\">dharma23</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 14, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">Totally unusable for complex websites, you need to purchase the PRO version since the free one doesn\'t have any shortcode.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Never again</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/flugtraeumer\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6f128f427227b2d31e2acf0f29380e3?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/d6f128f427227b2d31e2acf0f29380e3?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/flugtraeumer\" class=\"reviewer-name\">flugtraeumer</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 11, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">1: The older version has a lot of bugs. Even bugs wich are known since years are not solved or they return whith some updates.\n2: They change the markup almost with every update so that your CSS customization needs to be done again.\n3: The new version is useless for the german market since there is no translation for it.\n4: The support is poor.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">lo actualice y dejo de funcionar</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"1 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"1\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/durval2015\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/02fa43dea5a310b2235ac3e650d30aab?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/02fa43dea5a310b2235ac3e650d30aab?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/durval2015\" class=\"reviewer-name\">durval2015</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 4, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">lo actualice y dejo de funcionar !! y no tiene opcion de recuperar version anterior. un  desastre !! no lo recomiendo</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">An excellent solution to our requirements</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tonybell\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/16bd45e95d832e1f5311468734006f29?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/16bd45e95d832e1f5311468734006f29?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/tonybell\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tonybell</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 4, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">We needed a tool that would allow us to gather information about live music events in our region and publish them online. The information in the database would then be exported to a CSV file and manipulated into our monthly printed magazine - oh, and we needed the facility to allow registered users to add their own events.\n\nTo give you an idea of scale, we have at any one time over 4,000 live events spread across a potential 1,500 venues, many small clubs and pubs.\n\nWe tried most of the available WordPress events plugins both free and subscription based but settled on The Events Calendar because, although not perfect, it was the nearest and best fit for our requirements.  To qualify that, no out-of-the-box solution will be 100% there for a sprcific need - for that you need bespoke!\n\nSince purchasing TEC we have been very impressed by the quality of the support we get when we raise queries - its fast, friendly and reliable.  Seriously the support team are professional and passionate about their product.\n\nThe team at Grapevine have no hesitation in recommending the TEC suite of plugins.</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Only show in town, so you get what&#039;s there; dodgy fb-level data harvesting</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"3 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"3\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-empty\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jayceland\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a798b2fd1134403c5f9d5f0faadb616b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/a798b2fd1134403c5f9d5f0faadb616b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' /></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/jayceland\" class=\"reviewer-name\">jayceland</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">février 3, 2020</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\">I\'ve been using The Events Calendar for a few years now and it works pretty good. Adding a lot of entries is difficult through the entry form, but the CSV file import works quite well and I use that all the time. Unfortunately the import feature is one of the \"fringe\" features and I expect it to disappear at any update.\n\nMy biggest complaint is with the update to version 5.0. It asks if you can share da